#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn15.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn15.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 15 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 15 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: 2. Dutiyavagga → duggatavaggo (bj)
msgctxt "sn15.11:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn15.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Duggatasutta "
msgstr "11. In a Sorry State "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn15.11:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī. "

msgctxt "sn15.11:1.2"
msgid "Tatra kho … pe … "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn15.11:1.3"
msgid "“Anamataggoyaṃ, bhikkhave, saṃsāro. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, transmigration has no known beginning. "

msgctxt "sn15.11:1.4"
msgid "Pubbā koṭi na paññāyati avijjānīvaraṇānaṃ sattānaṃ taṇhāsaṃyojanānaṃ sandhāvataṃ saṃsarataṃ. "
msgstr "No first point is found of sentient beings roaming and transmigrating, hindered by ignorance and fettered by craving. "

msgctxt "sn15.11:1.5"
msgid "Yaṃ, bhikkhave, passeyyātha duggataṃ durūpetaṃ niṭṭhamettha gantabbaṃ: "
msgstr "When you see someone in a sorry state, in distress, you should conclude: "

msgctxt "sn15.11:1.6"
msgid "‘amhehipi evarūpaṃ paccanubhūtaṃ iminā dīghena addhunā’ti. "
msgstr "‘In all this long time, we too have undergone the same thing.’ "

msgctxt "sn15.11:1.7"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu … pe … "
msgstr "Why is that? Transmigration has no known beginning. … "

msgctxt "sn15.11:1.8"
msgid "yāvañcidaṃ, bhikkhave, alameva sabbasaṅkhāresu nibbindituṃ alaṃ virajjituṃ alaṃ vimuccitun”ti. "
msgstr "This is quite enough for you to become disillusioned, dispassionate, and freed regarding all conditions.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn15.11:1.9"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
